import React, { useContext, useEffect } from 'react'; import { styled } from '@mui/material/styles'; import Box from '@mui/material/Box'; import Paper from '@mui/material/Paper'; import Grid from '@mui/material/Grid'; import '../Styles/ProfileSection.css'; import UserContext from '../../context/user/UserContext' import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom'; import UpdateProfile from './UpdateProfile'; import ModalBox from './ModalBox'; export default function ProfileSection() { let navigate = useNavigate(); const context = useContext(UserContext); const {userinfo,fetchUserinfo} = context; useEffect(()=>{ if(localStorage.getItem('token')){ fetchUserinfo(); }else{ navigate('/login'); } },[]); const Item = styled(Paper)(({ theme }) => ({ backgroundColor: theme.palette.mode === 'dark' ? '#1A2027' : '#fff', ...theme.typography.body2, padding: theme.spacing(2), textAlign: 'center', color: theme.palette.text.secondary, })); return (
Username: {userinfo.username}
Role: {userinfo.usertype}
Name: {userinfo.name}
Gender: {userinfo.gender}
Phone: {userinfo.phone}
Date of Birth: {userinfo.dob?new Date(userinfo.dob).toDateString():'Add Date of Birth'}
Address: {userinfo.address}
Grade: {userinfo.grade}
) }
